            <p>
                One simple place to manage your classes, students, quizzes, tasks, and attendance.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
            <h3>Get Started Easily</h3>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span>Teacher</span>
                <strong>Create classes • Control everything</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span>Student</span>
                <strong>Join with a code • Learn & submit work</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
