        <h2>Why choose ClassTrack?</h2>
        <div class="grid">

            <div class="card">
                <h3>No Confusion with Roles</h3>
                <p>
                    If you create a class, you are the <b>Teacher</b>.
                    If you join with a code, you are a <b>Student</b>.
                    Everything is set automatically.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Easy Quizzes</h3>
                <p>
                    Teachers can create quizzes with multiple choice or written questions.
                    Students can take quizzes and see their results easily.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Assignments & Deadlines</h3>
                <p>
                    Share tasks with deadlines.
                    Students submit their work online and teachers can review and grade it.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Attendance Tracking</h3>
                <p>
                    Teachers can mark students as <b>Present, Late, or Absent</b>.
                    Students can always check their attendance status.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Safe & Reliable</h3>
                <p>
                    Your data is protected.
                    Only teachers and students of the class can access its content.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Simple & Clean Design</h3>
                <p>
                    A clean interface that works smoothly on any device,
                    making class management easy and stress-free.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

